程序包chat的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • 所有程序包

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component (implements java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable)
      • java.awt.Container
        • java.awt.Window (implements javax.accessibility.Accessible)
          • java.awt.Frame (implements java.awt.MenuContainer)
            • javax.swing.JFrame (implements javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants)
              • chat.CaptureScreen (implements java.awt.event.ActionListener)
              • chat.ChatFrame (implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.ItemListener, java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.lang.Runnable)
              • chat.PList (implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, javax.swing.event.ListSelectionListener)
    • java.lang.Thread (implements java.lang.Runnable)
      • chat.ChatFrame.acceptfilethread
